** First Fridays
------------------------------------------------------------


** Main Street Deleware
------------------------------------------------------------

June 2nd

Downtown Delaware is hosting this first Friday event with the theme 'Artful Spaces Tour '. The monthly downtown celebration will feature free children's activities and extended shopping and dining hours for everyone. On June 5, youngsters will be invited to add their artwork to downtown Delaware by decorating the sidewalks with original chalk drawings. Their work will be good practice for Main Street Delaware's July 3 First Friday celebration, which will feature their annual sidewalk chalk art competition.
Event Website >> (http://www.mainstreetdelaware.com/first-fridays.html)

