** Paddle Palooza
------------------------------------------------------------


** Alum Creek
------------------------------------------------------------

June 7th

The Ohio Department of Natural Resources (ODNR) will host the second annual Paddle Palooza Festival at Alum Creek State Park Beach on Sunday, June 7, from 12-5 p.m. This free event is a great opportunity for people to try a variety of different canoes and kayaks and learn stand-up paddleboarding (SUP). Experts will also be on hand to share information about local paddling activities and resources.

Event Website >> (http://ohiodnr.gov/news/post/odnr-to-host-second-annual-paddle-palooza-festival-at-alum-creek-state-park-beach)

