** Honey Bee Festival
------------------------------------------------------------

June 27th

Come out to Stratford Ecological Center for a celebration of Honey Bees and pollinators! This year our speakers and presentations will explore the importance of a healthy habitat for pollinators. Buy local honey from Ohio beekeepers, learn about bees and participate in exciting activities while enjoying a wonderful day on the farm!

